title: #106: The Life and Death of XXXtentacion with Aaron Bowden
description: Thank you for tuning in for another fun interesting episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli.  This episode, Ryan and Sam welcome back Aaron Bowden to discuss black magic in the rap game and the conspiracies around the life and death of Rapper XXXtentacion.  Thank you for your support!
